title: San Francisco/Fisherman's Wharf
name: In-N-Out Burger
content: Standard In-N-Out Burger, but it has the distinction of being the only one in the city.  They serve "fresh burgers" and fries cut straight from the potato in front of you... it's still fast food, but it's definitely better than the usual fare.  This place gets seriously packed but the line does tend to move quickly.
